title: 820-3662 no audio on headphone jack
message:
Hey,
i'm working on a Macbook Pro mid 2014 15" that came with no audio. Located a partial short on PP4V5_AUDIO_ANALOG, caused by U6201.
After replacing U6201 I got sound again with speakers but when i connect headphones to the audio jack i just get some deep "clicking noises" but no sound at all...
The macbook detects the headphones (in die sound settings).

Thank you

title: 820-3662 no audio on headphone jack
message: Yes, u6200 is good. After replacing U6201 and noticing the Jack problem I replaced it.

title: 820-3662 no audio on headphone jack
message: Headphones amplifier is embedded into U6201; try another chip.
